Ah cảm ơn bạn đã xác nhận lại! Vậy vì cả 2 function đều **tự open/close workbook bên trong** bằng đường dẫn file, flow sẽ là:

1. `ProcessOneID` → ghi data vào dest → **Save & Close**
2. Sau đó mới gọi `CopyDataByColumnName(destFile, ...)` và `FillDefaultValue(destFile, ...)`

Đây là code hoàn chỉnh, tương thích 100% với signature gốc của bạn:

---

## Module: `modExportByID`

```vba
Option Explicit

' ============================================================
'  PUBLIC ENTRY POINT — gọi từ PAD
'  Trả về "Success" hoặc "Error: <message>"
' ============================================================
Public Function ExportByID(ByVal SourcePath     As String, _
                           ByVal TemplatePath   As String, _
                           ByVal OutputFolder   As String, _
                           ByVal ColumnMapping  As String, _
                           ByVal DefaultMapping As String, _
                           ByVal colID          As Long) As String

    Dim wbSrc   As Workbook
    Dim wsSrc   As Worksheet
    Dim arr     As Variant
    Dim dict    As Object
    Dim lastRow As Long
    Dim lastCol As Long
    Dim i       As Long
    Dim pid     As String

    On Error GoTo ErrHandler

    ExportByID = "Success"

    With Application
        .ScreenUpdating = False
        .DisplayAlerts  = False
        .Calculation    = xlCalculationManual
        .EnableEvents   = False
    End With

    ' --- Mở source, đọc 1 lần vào array, đóng ngay ---
    Set wbSrc = Workbooks.Open(Filename:=SourcePath, _
                               ReadOnly:=True, _
                               UpdateLinks:=False)
    Set wsSrc = wbSrc.Sheets(1)

    lastRow = wsSrc.Cells(wsSrc.Rows.Count, colID).End(xlUp).Row
    lastCol = wsSrc.Cells(1, wsSrc.Columns.Count).End(xlToLeft).Column

    If lastRow < 2 Then
        wbSrc.Close False
        ExportByID = "Error: Source không có dữ liệu"
        GoTo Finalize
    End If

    arr = wsSrc.Range(wsSrc.Cells(1, 1), _
                      wsSrc.Cells(lastRow, lastCol)).Value

    wbSrc.Close False       ' Đóng ngay — array tồn tại độc lập
    Set wbSrc = Nothing

    ' --- Collect unique ID ---
    Set dict = CreateObject("Scripting.Dictionary")
    dict.CompareMode = vbTextCompare

    For i = 2 To lastRow
        pid = Trim(CStr(arr(i, colID)))
        If pid <> "" And Not dict.Exists(pid) Then
            dict.Add pid, Empty
        End If
    Next i

    If dict.Count = 0 Then
        ExportByID = "Error: Không tìm thấy ID nào"
        GoTo Finalize
    End If

    ' --- Loop từng ID, lỗi 1 ID không dừng loop ---
    Dim key As Variant
    For Each key In dict.Keys
        Call ProcessOneID(arr, CStr(key), TemplatePath, _
                          OutputFolder, ColumnMapping, DefaultMapping, colID)
        DoEvents
    Next key

    GoTo Finalize

ErrHandler:
    ExportByID = "Error [" & Err.Number & "]: " & Err.Description

Finalize:
    With Application
        .ScreenUpdating = True
        .DisplayAlerts  = True
        .Calculation    = xlCalculationAutomatic
        .EnableEvents   = True
    End With

End Function


' ============================================================
'  XỬ LÝ TỪNG ID
'  Không tạo temp file — ghi thẳng vào dest rồi gọi 2 function
' ============================================================
Private Sub ProcessOneID(ByRef arrData        As Variant, _
                         ByVal productID      As String, _
                         ByVal TemplatePath   As String, _
                         ByVal OutputFolder   As String, _
                         ByVal ColumnMapping  As String, _
                         ByVal DefaultMapping As String, _
                         ByVal colID          As Long)

    Dim wbDest   As Workbook
    Dim wsDest   As Worksheet
    Dim destFile As String
    Dim lastCol  As Long
    Dim i        As Long
    Dim j        As Long
    Dim destRow  As Long
    Dim hasData  As Boolean

    On Error GoTo ExitSub

    lastCol = UBound(arrData, 2)
    hasData = False

    ' Kiểm tra có data không trước khi tạo file
    For i = 2 To UBound(arrData, 1)
        If Trim(CStr(arrData(i, colID))) = productID Then
            hasData = True
            Exit For
        End If
    Next i

    If Not hasData Then Exit Sub

    ' --- Tạo dest file từ template ---
    If Len(Dir(OutputFolder, vbDirectory)) = 0 Then MkDir OutputFolder

    destFile = OutputFolder & "\Report_" & productID & "_" & _
               Format(Now, "yymmddhhnnss") & ".xlsx"

    FileCopy TemplatePath, destFile

    ' --- Mở dest, ghi data trực tiếp ---
    Set wbDest = Workbooks.Open(Filename:=destFile, UpdateLinks:=False)
    Set wsDest = wbDest.Sheets(1)

    ' Xác định dòng bắt đầu ghi
    If wsDest.Cells(1, 1).Value = "" Then
        ' Sheet trống — ghi header ở dòng 1
        For j = 1 To lastCol
            wsDest.Cells(1, j).Value = arrData(1, j)
        Next j
        destRow = 2
    Else
        ' Template đã có nội dung — ghi tiếp sau dòng cuối
        destRow = wsDest.Cells(wsDest.Rows.Count, 1).End(xlUp).Row + 1
    End If

    ' Ghi từng dòng khớp với productID
    For i = 2 To UBound(arrData, 1)
        If Trim(CStr(arrData(i, colID))) = productID Then
            For j = 1 To lastCol
                wsDest.Cells(destRow, j).Value = arrData(i, j)
            Next j
            destRow = destRow + 1
        End If
    Next i

    ' --- Save & Close trước khi gọi 2 function của bạn ---
    ' (vì chúng tự open/close bên trong)
    wbDest.Save
    wbDest.Close False
    Set wbDest = Nothing

    ' --- Gọi 2 function gốc của bạn --- 
    Call CopyDataByColumnName(destFile, destFile, ColumnMapping)
    Call FillDefaultValue(destFile, DefaultMapping)

    Exit Sub

ExitSub:
    ' Lỗi 1 ID → log ra file, KHÔNG stop loop
    On Error Resume Next
    If Not wbDest Is Nothing Then
        wbDest.Close False
        Set wbDest = Nothing
    End If

    Dim fNum As Integer
    fNum = FreeFile
    Open OutputFolder & "\export_errors.log" For Append As #fNum
    Print #fNum, Now & " | ID=" & productID & " | Err " & _
                 Err.Number & ": " & Err.Description
    Close #fNum
    On Error GoTo 0

End Sub
```

